ADP is hiring a Lead Application Developer for directing the development team in the design, development, coding, testing and debugging of applications for the Total Absence Management application suite. This position also ensures effective communication between team members and other IT functional areas. Additionally, will provide feedback and suggestions for process and product improvement and act as a technical mentor and adviser. 
